Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.93,0:02:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過亂七八糟得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.73,0:02:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乾杯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.23,0:02:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乾杯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.27,0:02:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣\N你們真的很不夠意思耶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.60,0:02:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,簡直差勁透了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.04,0:03:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為你太興奮了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.84,0:03:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過真是太好了﹐小石
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.41,0:03:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.59,0:03:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了？阿跨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.12,0:03:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無精打采的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.62,0:03:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概是因為那個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.62,0:03:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為只有自己沒有人陪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.53,0:03:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無法誠心的祝福別人\N感覺到自己器量的狹窄
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.76,0:03:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拼命的想要擠出一個笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.30,0:03:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,偏偏理性無法控制感性
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.77,0:03:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亦即﹐所謂的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.14,0:03:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不是這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.07,0:03:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說阿跨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.21,0:03:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就別想高攀瑞穗老師了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.61,0:03:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就近忍耐一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.24,0:03:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就近？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.92,0:03:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,森野的確長得很可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.62,0:03:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別喜歡上我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.42,0:03:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.46,0:03:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.03,0:04:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,漂介﹐你也是因為就近\N才跟我在一起的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.73,0:04:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不是呢﹐妳不要誤會
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.60,0:04:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.84,0:04:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.91,0:04:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你喜歡我哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.64,0:04:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真拿他們沒輒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.08,0:04:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.95,0:04:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然是因為“就近”的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.38,0:04:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.62,0:04:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,季節已經來到\N不需要這個的時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.32,0:04:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.13,0:04:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.56,0:04:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小桂的朋友\N那位個子小小的女生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.26,0:04:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她也得了同樣的病啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.30,0:04:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不想讓森野停滯下來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.37,0:04:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我非常了解小桂的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.74,0:04:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以這種狀況\N可能會持續一段時間
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.25,0:04:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.15,0:04:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然瑞穗老師都這麼說了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.28,0:04:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是﹐這樣好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.29,0:04:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是小桂所希望的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.76,0:05:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說小桂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.26,0:05:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這也是瑞穗老師妳所希望的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.46,0:05:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是個大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.07,0:05:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀﹐有什麼關係呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.44,0:05:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女人在心愛的人面前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.77,0:05:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稍微任性一點也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.84,0:05:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是﹐我是個老師
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.72,0:05:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊﹐你們進行得很順利是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.32,0:05:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.09,0:05:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼﹐謝謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.73,0:05:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.77,0:05:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了\N上次我說的是真的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.77,0:05:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把頭髮剪短﹐鬍鬚剃乾淨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.40,0:05:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定會很有女人緣的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.21,0:05:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.75,0:05:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了﹐瑞穗老師
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.78,0:06:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就先讓小桂住我這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.35,0:06:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.39,0:06:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託妳了…是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.48,0:06:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂﹐我是森野
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.51,0:06:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊﹐森野﹐是我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.92,0:06:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身體情況如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.32,0:06:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.65,0:06:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有發病的徵兆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.65,0:06:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.22,0:06:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.06,0:06:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,倒是﹐你自己呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.89,0:06:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在勉強你自己吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.43,0:06:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.26,0:06:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,緣川是個好女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.06,0:06:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身材也蠻不錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.17,0:06:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且她很喜歡我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.28,0:06:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.81,0:06:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有﹐沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.51,0:07:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,森野
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.38,0:07:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.45,0:07:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們要前進
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.72,0:07:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定要向前進
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.72,0:07:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯﹐是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.99,0:08:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以牽手嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.29,0:08:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.83,0:08:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得夏天就要結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.43,0:08:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好喜歡夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.84,0:08:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小桂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.17,0:08:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊﹐對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.67,0:08:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正夏天還會再來嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.08,0:08:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到了明年﹐一定會再來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.91,0:08:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.92,0:08:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.28,0:08:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今年的夏天﹐只有今年會來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.87,0:09:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忘了拿給他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.41,0:09:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小桂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.72,0:09:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂﹐我是森野
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.62,0:09:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊﹐是我﹐草薙桂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.22,0:09:24.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,草薙啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.89,0:09:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上下去﹐你等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.40,0:09:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不用這麼擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.97,0:09:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.74,0:09:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是還是會擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.27,0:09:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不相信我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.91,0:09:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為總覺得妳無法掌握
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.71,0:09:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊﹐對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.11,0:09:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就是這種個性
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.35,0:09:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或者應該說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.49,0:09:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自從生病之後\N變得有點喜歡挖苦人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.96,0:09:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白這種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.36,0:09:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.86,0:10:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊﹐你摸摸看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.06,0:10:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,心臟跳得很穩對不對？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.67,0:10:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.40,0:10:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好純情喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.54,0:10:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請妳說我是個有常識的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.71,0:10:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過﹐健康就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.91,0:10:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是真的這麼認為
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.88,0:10:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.81,0:10:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果能早一點認識你﹐我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.95,0:10:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定是老天爺讓我們相逢的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.75,0:10:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同病相憐的兩個人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.39,0:10:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,草薙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.43,0:10:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小桂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.66,0:10:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,緣川\N小石
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.16,0:10:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原…原來是這麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.93,0:10:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是的﹐妳誤會了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.94,0:10:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.20,0:10:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說謊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.11,0:10:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我知道\N你的心一直不在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.34,0:10:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觀察你很久了\N我看得出來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.98,0:10:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為你是一直忘不了\N之前喜歡的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.38,0:10:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果根本不是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.15,0:11:00.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根本不是這樣嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.92,0:11:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,緣川﹐緣川
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.72,0:11:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小石﹐小石
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.99,0:11:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行﹐不要停止
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.56,0:11:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,緣川的誤會﹐我會去說清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.46,0:11:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以妳千萬不要停滯！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.43,0:11:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我緣川可能會去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.96,0:11:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她果然在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.32,0:11:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是親密的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.96,0:11:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要開玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.29,0:11:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有這個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.40,0:11:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我過去找她
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.23,0:11:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好堅強喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.30,0:11:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.10,0:11:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.47,0:11:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過我的確希望變得堅強一點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.41,0:11:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.24,0:11:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小桂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.48,0:12:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳願意聽我說嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.65,0:12:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.75,0:12:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟森野的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.65,0:12:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實我只是去找她\N談妳的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.52,0:12:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才不相信呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.82,0:12:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那妳要我怎麼做？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.39,0:12:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼做妳才肯相信？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.53,0:12:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吻我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.17,0:12:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吻我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.08,0:12:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好﹐我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.56,0:12:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老…老師
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.63,0:12:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瑞穗老師
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.64,0:12:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小桂﹐你的手…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.07,0:13:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.58,0:13:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師﹐為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.75,0:13:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.15,0:13:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.92,0:13:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小桂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.73,0:13:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.36,0:13:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼瑞穗老師會哭呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.16,0:13:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.70,0:13:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起﹐緣川﹐我馬上回來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.57,0:13:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.07,0:13:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小桂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.04,0:13:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小石
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.31,0:13:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小苺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.71,0:13:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我全部跟妳說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.51,0:13:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不﹐我似乎非說不可
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.62,0:13:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我到底在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.69,0:13:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然會做這種事﹐真是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.39,0:13:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很笨﹐可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.00,0:13:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.60,0:14:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.54,0:14:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小桂跟小苺罹患同一種病？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.35,0:14:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.78,0:14:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽了妳跟草薙的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.78,0:14:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就在想\N妳一定哭得很傷心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.95,0:14:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的很受不了﹐所以就發病了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.16,0:14:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,草薙知道了以後﹐為了我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.30,0:14:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以他才會打電話給我
